  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a perspective multicentric study for the treatment of patients aged equal or less
      than 60 years and submitted to an allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation from an
      HLA compatible related or unrelated donor because affected by resistent or refractory or
      relapsed after autologous stem cell transplantation Ewing Sarcoma or Soft tissues sarcoma who
      did not benefit from conventional therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
