  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 0-60 years.

          -  Performance status according to Karnofsky score &gt; 70%

          -  Normal liver function

          -  Normal renal function

          -  Normal cardiac function

          -  Informed consent

          -  Availability of an HLA compatible Donor

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Absence of at least one of the inclusion criteria
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
